  <p class="body-text">"Unknown" attackers have been plaguing the <a href='https://www.start.umd.edu/gtd/' traget='_blank'>Global Terrorism Database</a> for years. Attacks have jumped higher than ever in the last few years.</p>
  <p class='body-text'>In its last few years, the database recorded a heightened number of total attacks, with more unknown attacks than ever. The increase of total attacks has been ongoing since 2011, when there were 10 attacks. In 2017, the most current year in the database, there were 65, over a 650% increase from 2011. The largest jump happened from 2015 to 2016.</p> 
